    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy and is in pristine condition\u2014it basically looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every single detail, and it\u2019s finally ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s as close to brand new as it gets, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
