    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This specimen represents the pinnacle of precision engineering, featuring a high-revving 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile six-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. Mechanically pristine, the engine maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, with a documented VANOS overhaul and reinforced subframe for structural longevity. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a meticulously maintained suspension geometry with fresh bushings and original-spec dampers, while the braking system features cross-drilled rotors and high-friction compound pads for consistent thermal management. This is a collector-grade example with zero fluid seepage, a flawless undercarriage, and a comprehensive service log, presenting in truly concours-ready condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
