      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen. The exterior features a flawless, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the deep metallic paint remains entirely free of swirls, scratches, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium hand-stitched leather upholstery shows no signs of compression or wear, and the bolsters remain firm and pristine. Every electronic component and interior surface, from the high-resolution displays to the brushed aluminum trim, is immaculate. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a meticulous, full-service history included. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never driven in inclement weather, and remains 100% original. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. Includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and a custom-fit breathable car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
