      "description": "We are proud to present this vehicle in exemplary, showroom condition. This unit has been curated for the most discerning clientele, exhibiting a level of preservation that is seldom seen on the secondary market. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to uncompromising excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that maintains its original integrity and peak performance standards.",
      "price": 46500.0,
