    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It's been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a scratch or a dent on it, and the interior is just flawless\u2014it honestly feels brand new. It's a total dream to drive and has been kept in such incredible shape. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make the next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
