    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant delivers linear torque through six individual throttle bodies, with the high-pressure VANOS system recently serviced for optimal valve timing. This specimen features a structurally reinforced rear subframe and a pristine Getrag six-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is anchored by a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a suspension refreshed with OEM bushings to maintain its razor-sharp turn-in. Finished in its original paint with verified thickness, the exterior is devoid of imperfections. This is a mechanically sorted, concours-standard example for the discerning collector who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and chassis rigidity.",
